    {
      "id": "PopularPost362069",
      "post_content": "[Aladdin's Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aladdin's Ring) and [Aladdin's Lamp](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aladdin's Lamp) are both prime targets both for the Poltergeist, both for their absurd cost and for the sheer WTF factor of beating an opponent to death with a brass lamp or, God forbid, a small ring.  \n  \nInteresting note: [Umbral Mantle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Umbral Mantle) allows him to possess multiple artifacts at once!",
      "posted_by": "Arachnos",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost362069\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Aladdin's Ring\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aladdin's Ring\">Aladdin's Ring</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Aladdin's Lamp\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aladdin's Lamp\">Aladdin's Lamp</a> are both prime targets both for the Poltergeist, both for their absurd cost and for the sheer WTF factor of beating an opponent to death with a brass lamp or, God forbid, a small ring.<br/><br/>Interesting note: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Umbral Mantle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Umbral Mantle\">Umbral Mantle</a> allows him to possess multiple artifacts at once!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '362069'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54910\">Arachnos</span>\r\n                                (2/5/2014 9:44:05 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRep